                  </persName>
             used to come there; he has been dead several years.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. ALLEY. Q. All your information is derived being desired to call out for such a person - A. Yes; there are some seats which have names on them, and some have names on their books which lay there. I know all who attend regularly; there are a great many.</p>

