               <p>Q. Now turn to the Primary; to the short abstract, do you see any entry there - A. Yes, (reads) Sir R. Peel to John (something illegible), the word Sir is considerably like his writing, but it is written on an erasure; there is nothing in the ledger entry to enable me to speak to the writing.</p>
